  "text": [
    "The old man",
    "drew the line",
    "for his son,",
    "the executive:",
    "\u201cI don\u2019t want you spending money on me!",
    "(not as long as there are fathers)\u201d,",
    "the line ageless",
    "as the independence of time.",
    "Musters tears",
    "and overflows",
    "the inner ear,",
    "yet does not matter.",
    "It can not cure frailty.",
    "I seek him",
    "who will seek me out",
    "and will believe",
    "what I do not believe",
    "(that is my frailty).",
    "\u201cSit down here with us,\u201d",
    "he says,",
    "\u201cYou don\u2019t have to impress anyone.",
    "Here is my hand.",
    "Your age is of no significance.\u201d",
    "Ah!",
    "I move closer to his mouth",
    "and look into his eyes.",
    "I do not avert mine,",
    "there is no reason to,",
    "or retreat",
    "into a kindly smile.",
    "Ah, companero,",
    "you were born",
    "on the wrong day",
    "when God was paradoxical.",
    "You\u2019ll have to",
    "find yourself an old dog."
  ],
  "title": "The Old Man Drew the Line",
  "year": ""
